    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master Mage <strong>Toshiro's</strong> past is fractured, and the broken fragments have come tumbling down at the worst moment. Now he must fight his way through the corrupted memories of his hardest years, relearning his most important lessons and rediscovering the friends that helped him along the way. Every new turn is a fight for survival as Toshiro reassembles years of his own timeline and strives to escape the dark forces that seem to stalk him obsessively, all before the sky falls and the Abyss claims his world forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eyes of the Sky</strong>’s combat is all about combining sword-work with magic. Enhance your sword combos with spells, each one offering unique utilities to expand your combat options, and become the ultimate spellsword! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180280/extras/1ec869a0106e5ffd530cf47ec8a99937.poster.avif?t=1762642226\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180280/extras/1ec869a0106e5ffd530cf47ec8a99937.webm?t=1762642226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180280/extras/1ec869a0106e5ffd530cf47ec8a99937.mp4?t=1762642226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >String together intricate combos to trigger <strong>form changes</strong>. The form you trigger depends on the types of moves you use, with each form offering a completely unique set of moves to diversify your combo potential!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180280/extras/66ce629314e98c295a496286535edfd6.poster.avif?t=1762642226\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180280/extras/66ce629314e98c295a496286535edfd6.webm?t=1762642226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180280/extras/66ce629314e98c295a496286535edfd6.mp4?t=1762642226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge powerful <strong>bosses</strong> that demand strategic openings and precise execution of your combos before they retaliate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180280/extras/7c9dfe75fa88124a0686fa187a437bee.poster.avif?t=1762642226\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180280/extras/7c9dfe75fa88124a0686fa187a437bee.webm?t=1762642226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180280/extras/7c9dfe75fa88124a0686fa187a437bee.mp4?t=1762642226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies and collect fragments to restore Toshiro's memories and unlock new abilities to unleash in battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180280/extras/8c35556b317c4009a69ccd75d702126c.poster.avif?t=1762642226\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\